ns]])\n|39\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|[[1930\u201331 Northern Rugby Football League season|1930\u201331]]\n| {{leagueicon|Swinton|16}} '''[[Swinton Lions|Swinton]]''' (3)\n| {{leagueicon|Leeds|16}} [[Leeds Rhinos|Leeds]]\n| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Eric Harris]] ({{leagueicon|leeds|16}} [[Leeds Rhinos|Leeds]])\n|58\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|[[1931\u201332 Northern Rugby Football League season|1931\u201332]]\n| {{leagueicon|St Helens|16}} '''[[St Helens R.F.C.|St. Helens]]'''\n| {{leagueicon|Huddersfield|16}} [[Huddersfield Giants|Huddersfield]]\n| [[Ernie Mills]] ({{leagueicon|huddersfield|16}} [[Huddersfield Giants|Huddersfield]])\n|50\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|[[1932\u201333 Northern Rugby Football League season|1932\u201333]]\n| {{leagueicon|Salford City|16}} '''[[Salford Red Devils|Salford]]''' (2)\n| {{leagueicon|Swinton|16}} [[Swinton Lions|Swinton]]\n| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Eric Harris]] ({{leagueicon|leeds|16}} [[Leeds Rhinos|Leeds]])\n|57\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|[[1933\u201334 Northern Rugby Football League season|1933\u201334]]\n| {{leagueicon|Wigan|16}} '''[[Wigan Warriors|Wigan]]''' (4)\n| {{leagueicon|Salford City|16}} [[Salford Red Devils|Salford]]\n| Brown ({{leagueicon|salford city|16}} [[Salford Red Devils|Salford]])\n|45\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|[[1934\u201335 Northern Rugby Football League season|1934\u201335]]\n| {{leagueicon|Swinton|16}} '''[[Swinton Lions|Swinton]]''' (4)\n| {{leagueicon|Warrington|16}} [[Warrington Wolves|Warrington]]\n| {{flagicon|WAL}} [[Jack Morley]] ({{leagueicon|Wigan|16}} [[Wigan Warriors|Wigan]])\n|49\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|[[1935\u201336 Northern Rugby Football League season|1935\u201336]]\n| {{leagueicon|Hull|16}} '''[[Hull F.C.]]''' (3)\n| {{leagueicon|Widnes|16}} [[Widnes Vikings|Widnes]]\n| {{flagicon|AUS}} [[Eric Harris]] ({{leagueicon|leeds|16}} [[Leeds Rhinos|Leeds]])\n|63\n|- style=\"background:#f5faff;\"\n|[[1936\u201337 Northern Rugby Football League sea